{"tid":1892884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小丑神主日崇拜","createTime":"2020-02-22T23:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T23:54:34.000Z","uid":86,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aa4db894839c107a690d81b9983decbbbc912c66","tid":1892884,"uid":86,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T23:22:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">坐直個人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PwFpt3H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPwFpt3H.jpg&h=862845d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們在連登的神，<br />\n<br />\n願人都尊神的名為膠；<br />\n<br />\n願神的國降臨；<br />\n<br />\n願神的旨意行在地上，<br />\n<br />\n如同行在登上。<br />\n<br />\n我們日用的正皮，<br />\n<br />\n求神今日賜給我們。<br />\n<br />\n又求饒恕我們的假膠，<br />\n<br />\n因為我們饒恕假膠的人。<br />\n<br />\n不叫我們遇見試探，<br />\n<br />\n拯救我們脫離耶教。<br />\n<br />\n因為連豬、連狗、連貓、<br />\n<br />\n全是神的，直到永遠。膠們。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f585db5029437da7e53bde5d66f6ed3f100b1a85","tid":1892884,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor